Class BundleDifference

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.BundleDifference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
    public class BundleDifference
extends AbstractXmlObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class used to contain the results of a comparison between two Bundle objects. These are calculated by the RoleLifecycler and displayed in role approval work items.
